## Naming Conventions

| Original Private Class | File Name | Public Class |
|------------------------|-----------|--------------|
| `_TabBar` | `orders_tab_bar.widget.dart` | `OrdersTabBar` |
| `_CategoryFilters` | `category_filters.widget.dart` | `CategoryFilters` |
| `_HeroImage` | `hero_image.widget.dart` | `HeroImage` |
